{"id": 1113, "genre": 1001, "title": "你会因为什么放弃一个游戏？", "description": "“想好好学习”只是你的借口，你不玩游戏的真正原因是？（题图来自：CACHETE JACK）", "record_count": 6097, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160710211243c9oesqpL13VY2vBR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-15T17:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 98560, "content": "腻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551644}, {"id": 98816, "content": "要玩那种有一点难度，又不太难，要动点脑子，又不太费脑子的游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679242}, {"id": 99584, "content": "朋友的离开，模式的厌倦，以往的游戏都是因为这两个。现在，也无所谓放不放弃了，因为真心玩的少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683372}, {"id": 98561, "content": "先工作再做人民币玩家", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678675}, {"id": 98562, "content": "累觉不爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 98818, "content": "太占用时间，强迫症不想错过任何一个活动，于是太累就删了", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681225}, {"id": 99074, "content": "16G狗必须删游戏腾内存。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628125}, {"id": 99330, "content": "下一个游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669481}, {"id": 100354, "content": "因为爱的人  不玩这个游戏了  玩它的目的只是为了拉进距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685061}, {"id": 98819, "content": "我FF13-2卡在一个时间线里出不去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605555}, {"id": 99075, "content": "他们都不在了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680021}, {"id": 100611, "content": "不磕金就成了炮灰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688240}, {"id": 98820, "content": "太笨玩的没有成就感", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681228}, {"id": 99844, "content": "难上手又没人教，始终不是大神", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684652}, {"id": 98821, "content": "因为焦虑，因为不安，因为没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681227}, {"id": 107269, "content": "烧钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713855}, {"id": 127749, "content": "弹出点亮新成就：已经连续在线一百小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810975}, {"id": 98566, "content": "每一关都差不多，没什么新意\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676789}, {"id": 98822, "content": "实名制", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529260}, {"id": 99078, "content": "套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 98567, "content": "他不在", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202644}, {"id": 98823, "content": "年纪大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666427}, {"id": 98568, "content": "翻墙流量没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642170}, {"id": 98824, "content": "游戏体验太差劲，优化太烂，又卡又烫手", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681230}, {"id": 99080, "content": "渐渐对所有游戏不敢兴趣了，只对实况足球还有念想。但是买个PS4只玩一个游戏也奢侈，也没人一起玩，平时事情也多，就渐渐啥都不玩了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681640}, {"id": 98569, "content": "因为我用的wp手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506300}, {"id": 98825, "content": "好游戏都收费", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672444}, {"id": 99081, "content": "玩腻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649931}, {"id": 99337, "content": "不要浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670813}, {"id": 98314, "content": "浪费时间…", "image": null, "praise_count": 426, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 98570, "content": "玩久了就觉得无聊", "image": "img/option/option/20160716115930i58xRgGvAIn63Sed.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680709}, {"id": 98826, "content": "玩到不想玩看了就觉得无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671378}, {"id": 99082, "content": "要么就是无聊不好玩，要么就是显得太深，熬打游戏夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654747}, {"id": 98315, "content": "已经没有多少时间让我玩了，我必须抓紧时间努力实现梦想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 270, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667432}, {"id": 98827, "content": "玩着玩着 游戏变得无聊了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511256}, {"id": 99083, "content": "因为我玩游戏不充钱（没钱）然后就开始被各种被嫌弃 不玩了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681643}, {"id": 98316, "content": "简直就是拖延症的催化剂，明明知道改休息，还是会玩到半夜三点", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 98572, "content": "画风和智力性都不够，很不新鲜", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620292}, {"id": 98828, "content": "没有人一起玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466437}, {"id": 98573, "content": "连跪。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680712}, {"id": 98829, "content": "没有了一起玩的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488640}, {"id": 99085, "content": "又有一个新游戏咯，刚好前一个又感觉没新鲜感了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670923}, {"id": 99341, "content": "心脏受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676610}, {"id": 98318, "content": "实在玩不下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598279}, {"id": 98574, "content": "它卖给腾讯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123049}, {"id": 98830, "content": "时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672507}, {"id": 98575, "content": "故意增加难度", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680718}, {"id": 98831, "content": "玩腻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681234}, {"id": 100623, "content": "肯定是在某一关过不去，关键是…攻略也找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}, {"id": 98320, "content": "游戏奖励机制不足，玩到后面没有动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387443}]}